Package pds.sitAnalyze Description

Analyzes the situation from object data provided by cvStores and decides what the ping pong table's current status is. This module looks not only at the immediate results, but also at an aggregation of the data. This way a singular erroneous result should be smoothed out by taking the rest of the data into account. Upon detecting a true change in status, it noti es the output module.
